1204
01:13:59,070 --> 01:14:00,390
Let's think then.

1205
01:14:00,390 --> 01:14:06,900
If I wanted to insert into this view,
what should I really do instead?

1206
01:14:06,900 --> 01:14:11,318
AUDIENCE: You should add it to the
collections table instead of the view.

1207
01:14:11,318 --> 01:14:12,610
CARTER ZENKE: I like that idea.

1208
01:14:12,610 --> 01:14:18,480
So I should add this row to the
