1209
01:14:18,480 --> 01:14:21,120
But now, here's a bit of a trick.

1210
01:14:21,120 --> 01:14:24,870
Let's say I add Farmers Working at Dawn.

1211
01:14:24,870 --> 01:14:27,030
We reacquired it.

1212
01:14:27,030 --> 01:14:34,630
What should I do in that case, when I'm
